name: BOOP
description: Our project is simple yet captivating: BOOP. Inspired by the delightful meme of touching a person’s or animal’s nose and saying 'BOOP!', our mission is to spread joy and fun throughout the Solana Ecosystem. At the heart of BOOP is our charming mascot, a blue cat with one goal: to BOOP every snoot it encounters across the blockchain. Join us as we add a playful touch to the world of crypto, one boop at a time!
